## Build artefacts (re-created by `dotnet build`)
bin/
obj/
*/publish/

## Backups produced by PoePatcher at runtime — stored alongside the GGPK
## the user pointed it at, never inside this repo
backups/

## Local extracts / inspector dumps from running against a live GGPK.
## These are output of running the tools — easy to regenerate, can be
## large (~2 MB for BaseItemTypes), and technically derived from the
## game's own copyrighted data so we don't want them in git regardless.
*.tsv
*.tsv.tmp
*.datc64
*.dat64
*.hlsl
*-inspect.txt
*-paths.txt
out/

## Proprietary Oodle DLL — see README. Users provide their own.
oo2core_*.dll
oo2core.dll

## Visual Studio / Rider / VS Code junk
*.user
*.suo
.vs/
.idea/
